[SPEAKER_01]: Just curious to know a little bit about you.

402
00:40:02,675 --> 00:40:06,157
[SPEAKER_01]: And then there'll be time after that, just if you have any questions for us.

403
00:40:07,707 --> 00:40:09,889
[SPEAKER_01]: just go ahead and share.

