00:42:30,177 --> 00:42:32,198
[SPEAKER_00]: I grew up in Medford my whole life.

437
00:42:32,418 --> 00:42:36,819
[SPEAKER_00]: I just retired as a sergeant from the Department of Corrections.

438
00:42:37,880 --> 00:42:43,061
[SPEAKER_00]: Years ago, I taught two and a half years at the vocational school.

439
00:42:43,081 --> 00:42:59,687
[SPEAKER_00]: I have a disabled adult child and it just makes me more aware of different disabilities that people aren't aware of unless they actually meet and get to know certain people.

440
