[SPEAKER_08]: And then when you look it up.

463
00:45:29,555 --> 00:45:31,196
[SPEAKER_08]: It's not low income housing.

464
00:45:33,236 --> 00:45:35,557
[SPEAKER_08]: And that's an issue that I have.

465
00:45:36,147 --> 00:45:48,914
[SPEAKER_08]: But I think the recreation department is doing a wonderful job with classes that it's offering to all types of disabilities and making modifications.

466
00:45:48,994 --> 00:45:51,135
[SPEAKER_08]: And I just really applaud them.

467
00:45:55,117 --> 00:45:58,699
[SPEAKER_08]: And really that's about it.

