00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:02,301
[SPEAKER_08]: I know that I've been at events in Medford

470
00:46:03,633 --> 00:46:13,159
[SPEAKER_08]: where I've talked to the disability boards that you have graciously attended, and I feel like people were listening when I talked to them.

471
00:46:14,920 --> 00:46:22,064
