[SPEAKER_01]: Heather, at the beginning of the meeting, and actually, and also the folks that are new to our meeting, we all introduced ourselves and just kind of shared, you know, our name and how long we've been on the commission and how long we've been in Medford and then what brought us to, what attracted us to join the commission.

