[SPEAKER_01]: And this was a bittersweet for her.

632
00:59:15,896 --> 00:59:18,838
[SPEAKER_01]: I think it was a hard choice.

633
00:59:19,498 --> 00:59:23,280
[SPEAKER_01]: And she says, it is with sadness that at this time I must resign

634
00:59:24,019 --> 00:59:27,505
[SPEAKER_01]: my position on the commission for persons with disabilities.

635
00:59:28,206 --> 00:59:36,017
