638
00:59:45,178 --> 00:59:49,702
[SPEAKER_01]: I thank you for this opportunity and look forward to joining you in future meetings.

639
00:59:50,603 --> 00:59:54,046
[SPEAKER_01]: Continue on with your great work for those in our community.

640
00:59:54,686 --> 00:59:55,067
